-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Candy Box 3 is an honorary, fan-made sequel to the Candy Box series. It adapts
game mechanics, UI conventions, and design ideas from:

  Candy Box 2
  Copyright (C) 2012 David "aniwey" L.
  Released under the GNU General Public License, version 3 or later.
  Source: http://candybox2.github.io/

Candy Box 2's source is used here only as a reference (kept out of this
repository, under reference/candybox2/, which is gitignored). Where Candy Box 3
reimplements or ports a Candy Box 2 mechanic — the progressive "request a
feature" GUI unlock, the eat/throw candy mechanics, the status bar and health
bar, the inventory, the quest/combat model — it does so as a derivative work
under the same GPL-3.0-or-later license. The original work is the creation of
